name: The Last Gate
overview: The Last Gate is a miscellaneous shooter for the Commodore 64. It was developed by DiBi Soft and published only in Italy in Next Game #04 (04/1985). In this game, you control a stationary tank in the middle of the screen, which can only move the tank's turret. Enemies come from all sides of the screen, so be careful where you aim your turret.
